@baseUrl = http://localhost:5180

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TELEMETRY
# Two modes:
#   - Snapshot  : single JSON response
#   - SSE stream: live updates (text/event-stream), keep connection open
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get Status Snapshot
# Returns current DroneStatus (state, position, heading, speed, battery …)
GET {{baseUrl}}/drone/status
Accept: application/json

###

### Telemetry Stream  (Server-Sent Events)
# Streams DroneStatus at the configured telemetry interval (1 s).
# Keep the connection open; close it to stop receiving events.
# Note: most REST clients show the raw event stream; use a browser
#       or EventSource client for a nicer experience.
GET {{baseUrl}}/drone/telemetry
Accept: text/event-stream

###
